      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is optimized for the driving purist, equipped with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The chassis benefits from refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining precise suspension geometry and turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its 'good' condition, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
